- Mau minum?
- Iya.

80
00:05:27,142 --> 00:05:29,644
Untuk... wanita cantik,

81
00:05:31,063 --> 00:05:32,146
wanita yang kuat,

82
00:05:32,531 --> 00:05:36,150
