134
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:51,429
<i>Jadi kau menikahiku untuk menyelamatkanku.</i>

135
00:08:52,781 --> 00:08:54,615
<i>Iya.</i>

136
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:57,385
